# Git Push Target (Client Repo)

- Repository: `seminar-client`
- Default working branch: `feature/jobs`
- Default push target: `origin feature/jobs`

## Commit/Push Guidance

- Create and push client-related commits to `feature/jobs`.
- Do not push client commits to `main` unless explicitly requested.
- If push is rejected (non-fast-forward), rebase on `origin/feature/jobs` and push again without force.
